{"tid":1562605,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"小花：大家沒要求買尼馬","createTime":"2019-09-12T05:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T06:17:26.000Z","uid":226925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"69f1690b18337af23cc4caebe55fdc21e0b81030","tid":1562605,"uid":226925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:27:06.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】巴塞隆拿球星美斯坦言不知道會方有沒有全力簽尼馬，但坦言對交易泡湯不感失望。<br />\n<br />\n巴塞隆拿今夏邀請尼馬回巢的轉會肥皂劇最後化泡影，一直有指球王美斯（Lionel Messi）不滿會方不著緊，及至日前，他終首度為此開腔，「我很希望尼馬能回來，説實話，我不知道巴塞隆拿是否竭盡全力去簽，但巴黎聖日耳門從來不是容易對付的談判對手。」<br />\n<br />\n對於老友沒能重返魯營球場，美斯表示不失望：「我對此不感到失望，我們有出色的陣容，足以應付不同賽事，沒尼馬同樣能做到。尼馬是世上最出色球員之一，有他的商業影響力，球會的整體影響力會有所提高。」<br />\n<br />\n美斯最後還否認球員推動會方簽回尼馬，「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家沒要求把尼馬買回來</span>，我們只是提出自己的意見而已。」"},{"pid":"ffcf33612576ddb8db660352f0428c35317d2462","tid":1562605,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:27:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f6e7a5a3c694f0a567c276fb89920e52a5383851","tid":1562605,"uid":226925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T06:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}